     Instead, cruise missiles and bombs will be primarily targeted at military facilities and sites known or suspected of holding nuclear, biological or chemical weapons components, during a three-day campaign, according to senior military officials.<br>
     &quot;The White House is only interested in putting on a show,&quot; said a disgruntled military source.<br>
     The pending attack has European and Arab allies uneasy, and administration officials fear that a high Iraqi death toll could subject the United States to even more international criticism. Daahhhhh!!!!!!!!!<br><br>
